The paper deals with supervised learning and active learning, which are both subfields of machine learning. The focus of the paper is on developing strategies for cost minimisation in the context of labelling data, which is a common problem in many machine learning applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
